line.comment: * DESCRIPTION: Shops for items of two categories: needed and wanted.
* A dynamic blacklist to avoid getting stuck in loops

line.text: '%s aborting command. Home base or player balance too low to run this command.'

line.comment: * If we are going to be out of cash then lets just skip it for this cycle.
* Start with our initial blacklist but clone it so when we add to
* blacklist here it is only temporary
* Find a station to buy from
* Now we try and buy any wanted items we still need.
* See if we got all the needed shopping done
* Move to sector close to our destination
* Buy this stuff from a shipyard
* We can't buy equpment or upgrades with drones
* This should fail if the ship has no free docking ports.
* Merge needed and wanted list to make sure we buy as much as possible from this station
